      "content": "Here are a few options to elevate your abstract's impact for a Nature submission. Focus on crisp, active language that frames your limitations as fundamental scientific discoveries. Instead of simply stating limitations, frame them as revealing the very mechanics of current AI. For example, consider opening with a declarative statement about the current state of AI knowledge that your work corrects or refines.",
